    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is equipped with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate known chassis stress points. The engine exhibits strong compression and linear power delivery through its six individual throttle bodies. While the exterior displays minor road-wear consistent with its driver status, the suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the precise handling characteristics expected of the E46 platform. A performance-oriented specimen ready for the canyon or the track.",
